<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Slumber2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Slumber,</orth> vb. to sleep: <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.432" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 432</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.4.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 4, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 255</bibl>. Metaphorically, == to be inactive: <cit><quote>you must not now s. in it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.78" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 6, 78</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if heaven s. while their creatures want,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 16</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>